message.raw:
Updated test suite and news
Added support for creating archives without any tracks
Made chromosome.start and chromosome.end based upon sequence
Made iter(chromosome) and chromosome.itercontinuous() yield supercontigs
  in sorted order (important for more than 10 supercontigs)
